{"type":"message","id":"cb5684b1","parentId":"94145355","timestamp":"2026-04-21T01:23:35.312Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see that the feishu plugin is `openclaw-lark` (version 2026.4.1) but its `enabled` is set to `false`. The backup scripts use a hardcoded app ID `cli_a93650c6fc785bce` to send messages.\n\nBut the kiit session is through the openclaw-lark plugin (which is enabled). The kiit session's messages come through that plugin.\n\nThe issue is that the backup scripts use the `cli_a93650c6fc785bce` app to send messages. But the kiit conversation is with the kiit bot, which uses the openclaw-lark plugin configuration.\n \nThe user is asking why they can't see these messages in their kiit conversation—they're getting the notifications through a separate backup bot channel instead of seeing them directly in the kiit chat where I'm responding. This points to the messages being delivered to a different endpoint or bot entirely, rather than appearing inline in the kiit conversation thread. sent via API to a separate conversation.\n\nTo fix this, the backup/evolver scripts need to use the same Feishu app that kiit uses. But looking at the config, the openclaw-lark plugin is enabled but the feishu entry is disabled. This is confusing.\n\nLet me think about what's happening. The kiit session is receiving messages via openclaw-lark. The Lark plugin has its own bot identity. The backup scripts are using `cli_a93650c6fc785bce` which is a different app.\n\nThe user wants messages to appear in the kiit chat directly. For this to work, the scripts need to send messages as the same bot that's running the kiit session.\n\nBut I don't see the openclaw-lark plugin configuration for app_id/app_secret. Let me check the openclaw-lark extension config."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_tgl90xyu6tnk_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-lark/\ncat ~/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-lark/package.json 2>/dev/null | head -5"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_tgl90xyu6tnk_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find ~/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-lark -name \"*.json\" -o -name \"*.yaml\" -o -name \"*.env\" 2>/dev/null | head -10; find ~/.openclaw/feishu -type f 2>/dev/null | head -10"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776734600048,"responseId":"063604881414b7f0124c32514df81bf0"}}
