{"type":"message","id":"1b5182ec","parentId":"5fa7ce41","timestamp":"2026-04-21T02:05:39.411Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now update backup.sh and evolver.sh to use this script instead of the raw curl commands. This way, both scripts will send messages through the same feishu app (kiit's app), and since kiit is the one receiving messages in the current conversation, HALEI should see them."},{"type":"text","text":"现在更新两个脚本，用这个统一发消息：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_uuc57rq9ezht_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/openclaw-backup/backup.sh","edits":[{"oldText":"  # ── Send Feishu notification ──────────────────────────────────────\n  APP_ID=\"cli_a93650c6fc785bce\"\n  APP_SECRET=\"I6PGaAjXEqMW81COlOcRzc7zpdd2qqOV\"\n  USER_OPEN_ID=\"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n\n  TOKEN_RESP=$(curl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal\" \\\n    -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n    -d \"{\\\"app_id\\\":\\\"$APP_ID\\\",\\\"app_secret\\\":\\\"$APP_SECRET\\\"}\")\n  ACCESS_TOKEN=$(echo $TOKEN_RESP | python3 -c \"import json,sys; print(json.load(sys.stdin).get('tenant_access_token',''))\")\n\n  if [ -n \"$ACCESS_TOKEN\" ]; then\n    NOTIF_MSG=\"✅ 每日备份完成\\n\\n📦 备份 → 已推送至 openclaw-backup\"\n    curl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/im/v1/messages?receive_id_type=open_id\" \\\n      -H \"Authorization: Bearer $ACCESS_TOKEN\" \\\n      -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n      -d \"{\n        \\\"receive_id\\\":\\\"$USER_OPEN_ID\\\",\n        \\\"msg_type\\\":\\\"text\\\",\n        \\\"content\\\":\\\"{\\\\\\\"text\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"$NOTIF_MSG\\\\\\\"}\\\"\n      }\" > /dev/null 2>&1\n    echo \"[$(date)] Backup Feishu notification sent\"\n  else\n    echo \"[$(date)] Failed to get access token, skipping Feishu notification\"\n  fi\n  # ── End Feishu notification ────────────────────────────────────────","newText":"  # ── Send Feishu notification ──────────────────────────────────────\n  SCRIPT_DIR=\"$(cd \"$(dirname \"$0\")\" && pwd)\"\n  node \"$SCRIPT_DIR/send-to-me.js\" \"✅ 每日备份完成\\n📦 备份 → 已推送至 openclaw-backup\" && echo \"[$(date)] Backup Feishu notification sent\" || echo \"[$(date)] Failed to send Feishu notification\"\n  # ── End Feishu notification ────────────────────────────────────────"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776737124084,"responseId":"06360e6491c2ed532eb6c33e4b43ddf3"}}
