{"type":"message","id":"d04bb9e5","parentId":"9048f1ca","timestamp":"2026-04-21T13:49:09.672Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"SearXNG API is well-known - it's a search engine that provides a JSON API. The basic search endpoint is:\n\nGET/POST to `http://localhost:8888/search?q=query&format=json`\n\nThe API documentation shows:\n- `/config` - GET configuration\n- Search endpoint - GET/POST `/search?q=...&format=json`\n\nThe search API supports:\n- `q` - query\n- `format` - json (or html, csv, etc.)\n- `engines` - limit to specific engines\n- `categories` - filter by category\n- `lang` - language\n- `safesearch` - 0, 1, 2\n\n\n- `time_range` - day, week, month, year\n\nNow I'll create the skill by first initializing it with the creation script, then setting up the necessary files."},{"type":"text","text":"SearXNG API 格式已经清楚了。开始写 skill，先初始化：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mub88iqxk2ki_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/skill-creator/scripts/init_skill.py searxng-search --path /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776779341912,"responseId":"0636b34e73bf577b254f49296a8ceddd"}}
