{"type":"message","id":"83b59ac9","parentId":"29445c20","timestamp":"2026-04-21T14:09:11.363Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good - the SearXNG instance is running and accessible. The /config endpoint works (returned a huge JSON with all engine configurations). The issue was that /search requires JSON format but might have been blocked due to outgoing requests settings.\n\nLet me check the `outgoing` settings - by default SearXNG may block outgoing requests from bots. Looking at the limiter config:\n```json\n\"limiter\": {\n  \"botdetection.ip_limit.link_token\": false,\n  \"botdetection.ip_lists.pass_searxng_org\": true,\n  \"enabled\": false\n}\n```\n\nThe limiter is disabled, which is good.\n\nThe 403 on /search might be because:\n1. There's a network restriction (the SearXNG server can't reach out to the engine backends from its network)\n\n\n2. The engines need API keys that haven't been configured yet\n\nI should try adjusting the `search` parameter format. The config shows no API keys are required for the basic engines like Google, Bing, and DuckDuckGo, so the issue is likely network connectivity from the SearXNG instance rather than authentication.\n\nThe 403 Forbidden error might stem from missing CSRF headers or the instance needing proper initialization through its web UI first."},{"type":"text","text":"实例通了，`/config` 返回了完整的引擎列表。但 `/search` 403——很可能是 SearXNG 默认开启了 **outgoing 请求限制**，或者需要先在 UI 里完成初始设置。\n\n两个排查方向：\n\n**1. 检查 SearXNG 管理面板**\n访问 `http://192.168.31.146:8888/admin/settings` → 找 `outgoing` 相关设置，看是否有域名/API限制\n\n**2. 看容器日志**\n```bash\ndocker logs searxng --tail 30\n```\n看搜索引擎请求时报什么错\n\n---\n\n另外，你开启了哪些引擎？目前 config 里看到 Google、Bing、DuckDuckGo 等都显示 `enabled: true`，但 403 说明请求被拦截了，很可能是在等网络打通或者要配置 `use_external_openapi` 的设置。\n\n你先跑一下 docker logs 看看有没有线索？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776780531443,"responseId":"0636b7f48b1501818258aa10fd3c9830"}}
