{"type":"message","id":"a27f0406","parentId":"b8a368cb","timestamp":"2026-04-21T14:15:47.920Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There are two issues:\n1. `public_instance: true` is now active but requires the limiter, which needs Valkey/Redis\n2. DuckDuckGo times out (network issue to `html.duckduckgo.com`)\n\nThe `limiter` requires Valkey. But for now, let's try a simpler fix - instead of `public_instance: true`, we can use a different approach. \n\nActually, looking at the error more carefully - the limiter needs Valkey. We have two options:\n1. Install and configure Valkey for the limiter\n2. Keep `public_instance: false` and find another way to allow API access\n\n\n3. \nThe simplest approach might be adjusting the 403 issue differently - I could enable `enable_http: true` on the engines themselves, or modify the `server.limiter` setting. But really, the core problem is that with `public_instance: false`, the API endpoint `/search` is blocked for unauthenticated requests, whereas with `public_instance: true` it gets routed through the limiter which requires Valkey to function properly.\n\nLooking at the logs, the limiter fails without Valkey and then worker-1 crashes. The cleanest fix would be setting up Valkey as a sidecar container for SearXNG, though I could also try rolling back `public_instance` to false and exploring alternative solutions."},{"type":"text","text":"有两个问题同时出现：\n1. 开启 `public_instance: true` 后触发了 limiter，需要 Valkey（Redis 类）但没有\n2. DuckDuckGo 引擎网络超时\n\n先解决 Valkey——它是 limiter 的必需组件。给它配一个 sidecar：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_omcbvd0jlmv7_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"docker run -d \\\n  --name searxng-valkey \\\n  -p 6379:6379 \\\n  -v /etc/localtime:/etc/localtime:ro \\\n  valkey/valkey:8 \\\n  valkey-server --bind 0.0.0.0 --port 6379"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776780934281,"responseId":"0636b98612c655d8c3d800121a2a2809"}}
