{"type":"message","id":"63e2d09e","parentId":"cf0bc472","timestamp":"2026-04-21T14:17:25.701Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good progress! The SearXNG is working - it returned 429 Too Many Requests which means it's actually processing requests. The limiter is active. The 429 is expected because the limiter is in effect and we're hitting it from the same IP.\n\nLet me check if we can bypass the limiter by connecting from a different context, or if the limiter needs to be configured with the correct IP."},{"type":"text","text":"有进展！SearXNG 在跑了，返回 429 是 limiter 在拦你本机 IP 的请求。这是正常的——limiter 检测到来自同一个 IP 的频繁访问所以触发了限速。\n\n从容器内部测：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1ingir1061k4_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"docker exec searxng wget -O - \"http://127.0.0.1:8080/search?q=openclaw&format=json&limit=3\" --header \"X-Forwarded-For: 1.2.3.4\" 2>&1 | head -30"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776781036739,"responseId":"0636b9ed46f038b3cb9ca9b1a7bd1d1e"}}
