{"type":"message","id":"b636f765","parentId":"68880cbe","timestamp":"2026-04-21T14:22:48.127Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Docker Hub 访问超时。这台机器访问 docker.io 不稳定。既然最新的 searxng 镜像已经在本地了（latest 标签，之前拉过了），让我直接用本地的最新镜像重启，但不用 limiter。关键是：- 最新镜像：searxng/searxng:latest（已经在本地）\n- 不用 public_instance=true / limiter=true 的组合\n- 只需要 public_instance=false（当前默认）就能让 API 正常工作让我先确认一下，当前配置（public_instance=false, limiter=false）下是否还有其他问题导致 403。之前问题是：配置了 SEARXNG_LIMITER=true 环境变量导致 limiter 一直被启用。现在已经去掉了这个环境变量，但容器重启后还是 403。可能是之前的 volume 配置已经保留了设置。让我检查一下 volume 里的实际配置。"},{"type":"text","text":"Docker Hub 抽风。先用本地已有的 latest 镜像重启，去掉 limiter 相关设置：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rxqb95qvvnkc_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"docker run -d \\\n  --name searxng \\\n  -p 8888:8888 \\\n  -e SEARXNG_BASE_URL=\"http://192.168.31.146:8888/\" \\\n  -v searxng-config:/etc/searxng \\\n  --restart unless-stopped \\\n  searxng/searxng:latest\n\nsleep 6\ndocker logs searxng --tail 5"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776781357395,"responseId":"0636bb2da3a8cd8e3110f8d86014ac91"}}
