{"type":"message","id":"add4d897","parentId":"9cdf2686","timestamp":"2026-04-21T14:33:37.532Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_zcbdi0x2fo7l_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Note: Unnecessary use of -X or --request, POST is already inferred.\n*   Trying 127.0.0.1:8888...\n  % Total    % Received % Xferd  Average Speed   Time    Time     Time  Current\n                                 Dload  Upload   Total   Spent    Left  Speed\n\r  0     0    0     0    0     0      0      0 --:--:-- --:--:-- --:--:--     0* Connected to 127.0.0.1 (127.0.0.1) port 8888 (#0)\n> POST /search HTTP/1.1\r\n> Host: 127.0.0.1:8888\r\n> User-Agent: curl/7.81.0\r\n> Accept: */*\r\n> Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded\r\n> Content-Length: 30\r\n> \r\n} [30 bytes data]\n* Empty reply from server\n\r100    30    0     0  100    30      0  40000 --:--:-- --:--:-- --:--:-- 30000\n* Closing connection 0\ncurl: (52) Empty reply from server"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":18,"aggregated":"Note: Unnecessary use of -X or --request, POST is already inferred.\n*   Trying 127.0.0.1:8888...\n  % Total    % Received % Xferd  Average Speed   Time    Time     Time  Current\n                                 Dload  Upload   Total   Spent    Left  Speed\n\r  0     0    0     0    0     0      0      0 --:--:-- --:--:-- --:--:--     0* Connected to 127.0.0.1 (127.0.0.1) port 8888 (#0)\n> POST /search HTTP/1.1\r\n> Host: 127.0.0.1:8888\r\n> User-Agent: curl/7.81.0\r\n> Accept: */*\r\n> Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded\r\n> Content-Length: 30\r\n> \r\n} [30 bytes data]\n* Empty reply from server\n\r100    30    0     0  100    30      0  40000 --:--:-- --:--:-- --:--:-- 30000\n* Closing connection 0\ncurl: (52) Empty reply from server","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776782017517}}
{"type":"message","id":"6039831a","parentId":"add4d897","timestamp":"2026-04-21T14:33:52.639Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Empty reply from server on POST too. But HTML search works. The issue might be that `method: POST` combined with the `http_protocol_version: \"1.0\"` setting causes problems with HTTP/1.0 when the server closes connections immediately.\n\nActually wait - `http_protocol_version: \"1.0\"` forces HTTP/1.0 which doesn't support chunked transfer encoding or keep-alive. When curl sends a POST request and the server tries to respond with HTTP/1.0, it might close the connection immediately after sending the response.\n\nBut the HTML search works with GET... Let me think.Actually, HTML search from the container works (`wget` inside the container). But from the host - does HTML search work? Earlier when I ran `curl -s \"http://127.0.0.1:8888/search?q=openclaw\"` it returned empty too.Let me just check if the port mapping is actually working:```$ ss -tlnp | grep 8888LISTEN 0      4096         0.0.0.0:8888       0.0.0.0:*```But `curl -v http://127.0.0.1:8888/search?q=test` gets empty reply.The port 8888 is listening but not responding properly. This could be an iptables/firewall issue, or the docker proxy is having issues.\n\nLet me try a different approach - use docker exec to run Python inside the container and test the search API from within:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1v0fof6eynml_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"docker exec searxng python3 -c \"\nimport urllib.request, json, sys\nurl = 'http://127.0.0.1:8080/search'\ndata = urllib.parse.urlencode({'q': 'openclaw', 'format': 'json', 'limit': 2})\nreq = urllib.request.Request(url, data=data.encode(), method='POST')\nreq.add_header('Content-Type', 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded')\nreq.add_header('User-Agent', 'Mozilla/5.0')\ntry:\n    with urllib.request.urlopen(req, timeout=10) as r:\n        body = r.read()\n        print('Status:', r.status)\n        print('Body:', body[:500])\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print('Error:', e)\n\" 2>&1 | head -10"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776782017536,"responseId":"0636bdc2a68589c8f1fa5a2c3ca3e5eb"}}
