{"type":"message","id":"4d1a7d5c","parentId":"a9b20037","timestamp":"2026-04-21T14:40:30.417Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The searxng container doesn't have basic tools. The `bind_address: \"127.0.0.1\"` override from env didn't work, and the worker is crashing (connection refused means port isn't listening). Let me try without the `searxng/searxng:latest` image which has these granian/Python issues.\n\nActually, the fundamental issue is:\n1. The latest searxng image (2026.4.17) has a bug where enabling public_instance or its features cause granian to crash on shutdown\n2. When public_instance is false, the JSON API is blocked for non-localhost requests\n3. The container's settings are controlled by the image defaults + env vars, and env vars aren't properly overriding the settings\n\n\n4. I need to fix the settings inside the container before it starts the worker, or use a different approach entirely\n\nLet me try a different approach - copy a pre-made settings.yml file into the container at runtime to avoid these environment variable issues altogether."},{"type":"text","text":"环境变量没有正确覆盖配置。问题在于 `public_instance: false` 阻止 JSON API，启用又让 granian 崩溃。\n\n写一个正确配置的 settings.yml 直接替换进去：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_r5xbgsuou939_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/searxng-settings.yml","content":"general:\n  debug: false\n  instance_name: \"KIIT Search\"\n  privacypolicy_url: false\n  donation_url: false\n  contact_url: false\n  enable_metrics: true\n  open_metrics: ''\n\nbrand:\n  docs_url: https://docs.searxng.org/\n  public_instances: https://searx.space\n  wiki_url: https://github.com/searxng/searxng/wiki\n  issue_url: https://github.com/searxng/searxng/issues\n\nsearch:\n  safe_search: 0\n  autocomplete: \"\"\n  autocomplete_min: 4\n  favicon_resolver: \"\"\n  default_lang: \"zh-CN\"\n\nserver:\n  port: 8888\n  bind_address: \"0.0.0.0\"\n  limiter: false\n  public_instance: true\n  secret_key: \"KiitSearch2024SecretKey\"\n  image_proxy: false\n  http_protocol_version: \"1.1\"\n  method: \"GET\"\n\noutgoing:\n  request_timeout: 10.0\n  max_request_timeout: 15.0\n  pool_connections: 100\n  pool_maxsize: 20\n  enable_http2: true\n\nvalkey:\n  url: false\n\nui:\n  default_theme: simple\n  center_alignment: false\n  default_locale: \"zh-CN\"\n  results_on_new_tab: false\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776782416254,"responseId":"0636bf50eef3ea76fa420d3bc9b33a8f"}}
