{"type":"message","id":"08d2dff0","parentId":"dfa7da5d","timestamp":"2026-04-21T14:40:46.640Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to stop the container, copy this settings.yml into the container's volume or use a bind mount, and restart. The key setting is `public_instance: true` + `limiter: false` + `bind_address: \"0.0.0.0\"` + `method: \"GET\"`.\n\nBut the problem with public_instance: true is that it crashes with the granian worker. This might be because `public_instance: true` triggers something in the bot detection that requires the limiter, and the limiter requires valkey. \n\nWait, let me re-read the error more carefully:\n```\n2026-04-21 14:14:29,064 WARNING[searx.botdetection.config: missing config file: /etc/searxng/limiter.toml\n\n\n```\n\nI think the crash happens because when public_instance is true, it starts the limiter even though I disabled it. The limiter needs a limiter.toml file that doesn't exist, and if it can't connect to valkey, the worker crashes. The granian + Python 3.14 threading issue is a secondary problem. Let me check if setting `public_instance: true` + `limiter: false` without the valkey requirement resolves this, or if I need to create a minimal limiter.toml file instead.\n\nLooking at the logs more carefully, the crash shows the worker exited with code 1 and granian shut down, but the container kept running. The \"Unexpected exit from worker-1\" error suggests granian couldn't restart the worker after it crashed. With public_instance enabled and no limiter.toml, the botdetection warning appears but shouldn't cause a crash on its own. Maybe the real issue is that the worker is crashing for a different reason when handling requests, and the limiter.toml just happens to be the first warning in the log.\n\nActually, I should step back. The WSL2 environment with Docker port mapping seems to have fundamental issues with HTTP connections timing out. Rather than keep tweaking SearXNG settings in this broken environment, the practical solution is to have HALEI run SearXNG directly on Windows where it's already working at `http://192.168.31.146:8888`.\n\n```"},{"type":"text","text":"这个 Linux 环境的 Docker 网络有兼容性问题，继续调下去效率太低。你 Windows 上那个 `http://192.168.31.146:8888` 已经跑着了，我们直接用那个。\n\n更新 skill 的默认地址：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_epcmxvoruc7t_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/searxng-search/SKILL.md","edits":[{"oldText":"    --host | SearXNG 地址，默认 `http://localhost:8888`","newText":"    --host | SearXNG 地址，默认 `http://192.168.31.146:8888`"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776782430449,"responseId":"0636bf5ee97aee1d10baf90d2fadf45b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5e15abd1","parentId":"08d2dff0","timestamp":"2026-04-21T14:40:46.724Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_epcmxvoruc7t_1","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"edit\",\n  \"error\": \"Could not find the exact text in /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/searxng-search/SKILL.md. The old text must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines.\\nCurrent file contents:\\n---\\nname: searxng-search\\ndescription: SearXNG 元搜索引擎搜索。当用户需要搜索网络信息时使用，支持指定引擎、语言、时间范围、分类。不需要 API key，完全私有。支持普通搜索、图片搜索、新闻搜索。触发场景：(1) 用户说\\\"搜索一下...\\\"、\\\"帮我查一下...\\\" (2) 需要多引擎聚合结果时 (3) 替代 Google/Bing 单引擎搜索。\\n---\\n\\n# SearXNG Search Skill\\n\\n通过自托管的 SearXNG 实例进行聚合搜索，完全私有，不追踪，不依赖商业搜索引擎 API。\\n\\n## 快速使用\\n\\n```bash\\npython3 /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/searxng-search/scripts/search.py \\\"搜索内容\\\"\\n```\\n\\n## 核心参数\\n\\n| 参数 | 说明 |\\n|------|------|\\n| `--host` | SearXNG 地址，默认 `http://localhost:8888` |\\n| `--engines` | 指定引擎，逗号分隔，如 `google,bing` |\\n| `--categories` | 指定分类，如 `general,images` |\\n| `--lang` | 语言，如 `zh`、`en`、`all` |\\n| `--time-range` | 时间范围：`day`、`week`、`month`、`year` |\\n| `--limit` | 结果数量，默认 10 |\\n\\n## SearXNG 实例部署\\n\\nDocker 部署（已配置国内镜像）：\\n\\n```bash\\ndocker run -d \\\\\\n  --name searxng \\\\\\n  -p 8888:8888 \\\\\\n  -e SEARXNG_BASE_URL=\\\"\\n... (truncated)\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"edit","error":"Could not find the exact text in /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/searxng-search/SKILL.md. The old text must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines.\nCurrent file contents:\n---\nname: searxng-search\ndescription: SearXNG 元搜索引擎搜索。当用户需要搜索网络信息时使用，支持指定引擎、语言、时间范围、分类。不需要 API key，完全私有。支持普通搜索、图片搜索、新闻搜索。触发场景：(1) 用户说\"搜索一下...\"、\"帮我查一下...\" (2) 需要多引擎聚合结果时 (3) 替代 Google/Bing 单引擎搜索。\n---\n\n# SearXNG Search Skill\n\n通过自托管的 SearXNG 实例进行聚合搜索，完全私有，不追踪，不依赖商业搜索引擎 API。\n\n## 快速使用\n\n```bash\npython3 /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/s